text: Abdul Momin Mondol is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the incumbent Member of Parliament of Sirajganj-5. ==Early life== Mondol was born on 1 January 1980. He has a B.B.A. degree. ==Career== Mondol was elected to parliament from Sirajganj-5 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate 30 December 2018. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:11th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:1980 births Category:People from Sirajganj District
